                            FMSHRC PRIVACY POLICY

   The Federal Mine Safety and Health Review Commission will collect no
   personal information about you when you visit our website unless you
   choose to provide that information. The only information the Commission
   automatically collects is the visitors Internet domain and Internet
   Protocol address, the type of browser and operating system used to
   access the site, the file visited and the time spent in each file, and
   the time and date of the visit.
